      "comment": "PRINCESS ENERGY (6) has a solid record despite not breaking through for a win in 15 starts. Was below best latest when fourth (36.45) at this track but did hit the frame the start prior. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Worth another chance. SAMJAI (1) was in traffic and took a tumble last time at Gosford but was placed in a Maiden the start prior. No luck latest and can bounce back. REBEL FLARE (8) profiles nicely for her debut but has a wide box to overcome. Can kick off with a good run. SHINING GIRL (7) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
